Common Complexities

| Complexity | Example                    | Scales Well?              |
| ---------- | -------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| O(1)       | Hash lookup (average case) | ✅ Excellent               |
| O(log n)   | Binary Search              | ✅ Excellent               |
| O(n)       | Single traversal           | ✅ Good                    |
| O(n log n) | Merge Sort                 | ✅ Good                    |
| O(n²)      | Nested loops               | ⚠️ Acceptable for small n |
| O(2ⁿ)      | Naive recursion            | ❌ Poor                    |
| O(n!)      | Permutations               | ❌ Very poor               |


